  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One and a half years with Professor [NON-ENGLISH], went out to do some field work for my-- for my thesis, and found that the amount of material was so skimpy, almost nonexistent, that it was-- it became obvious to me immediately that you can't write a doctorate on such skimpy material.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You can write an article in the paper about it, but you can't write a doctorate, and especially in economic history, which talks about economic figures, and tables, and relative developments, and so on.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- there was nothing for me to handle, even though I knew-- I knew my history.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I knew my basic economics.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- the first year I've spent in-- in discussion with my group, and so on, and I held my own, even though they have had five years of economics and I'd had an arts subject.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But that was the end, regrettably, that I could-- I have never finished my doctorate in that subject.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] after-- after I've given that up, people who read my two essays-- the BA and the master's-- insisted, started to insist, that I should publish it, that I should-- that this sort of material ought to be published.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And until a couple of years ago, when Professor [NON-ENGLISH], [NON-ENGLISH], who is an old friend of mine, came one day to me and said, can I have-- can I have your manuscript?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I want to read them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I've heard about them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he came back after he read them and started abusing me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He said, and you are sitting on such material and not publishing it?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He called me every name under the sun.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he took the initiative to start pushing for some people to publish it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it's a long story.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
